Recruitment Executive
Responsibilities
JOB RESPONSIBILITIES:Execute the recruitment process from A to Z and not limited into sourcing, desk screening, interview, user interview, and recruitment pipeline reportLiaise with users for the recruitment process in pipeline (hearing session, endorsement, follow up, and ensure the successful candidate on board)REQUIREMENTS:S1 Degree from any majorAt least 4 years working experience in recruitment, preferably for start up company or medium - big scale company Having exposure in executive search / head hunter / recruitment agency is an advantageActive in English (both of oral and written) is mandatory and able to deal with expatriates or senior management levelMultitasking person, flexible, passionate, and willing to learn new things
